Qul innam_a_ _h_arrama rabbiya alfaw_ah_isha m_a_ \_th_\ahara minh_a_ wam_a_ ba_t_ana wa*a*l-ithma wa*a*lbaghya bighayri al_h_aqqi waan tushrikoo bi*A*ll_a_hi m_a_ lam yunazzil bihi sul_ta_nan waan taqooloo AAal_a_ All_a_hi m_a_ l_a_ taAAlamoon*a*
