Y_a_ banee _a_dama imm_a_ ya\tiyannakum rusulun minkum yaqu_ss_oona AAalaykum _a_y_a_tee famani ittaq_a_ waa_s_la_h_a fal_a_ khawfun AAalayhim wal_a_ hum ya_h_zanoon*a*
Wa*a*lla_th_eena ka_thth_aboo bi-_a_y_a_tin_a_ wa*i*stakbaroo AAanh_a_ ol_a_-ika a_s_-_ha_bu a*l*nn_a_ri hum feeh_a_ kh_a_lidoon*a*
