Awalam yan\_th_\uroo fee malakooti a*l*ssam_a_w_a_ti wa*a*l-ar_d_i wam_a_ khalaqa All_a_hu min shay-in waan AAas_a_ an yakoona qadi iqtaraba ajaluhum fabi-ayyi _h_adeethin baAAdahu yu\minoon*a*
