Wa-in tadAAoohum il_a_ alhud_a_ l_a_ yasmaAAoo watar_a_hum yan\_th_\uroona ilayka wahum l_a_ yub_s_iroon*a*
Khu_th_i alAAafwa wa\mur bi*a*lAAurfi waaAAri_d_ AAani alj_a_hileen*a*
Wa-imm_a_ yanzaghannaka mina a*l*shshay_ta_ni nazghun fa*i*staAAi_th_ bi*A*ll_a_hi innahu sameeAAun AAaleem*un*
Inna alla_th_eena ittaqaw i_tha_ massahum _ta_-ifun mina a*l*shshay_ta_ni ta_th_akkaroo fa-i_tha_ hum mub_s_iroon*a*
Wa-ikhw_a_nuhum yamuddoonahum fee alghayyi thumma l_a_ yuq_s_iroon*a*
Wa-i_tha_ lam ta\tihim bi-_a_yatin q_a_loo lawl_a_ ijtabaytah_a_ qul innam_a_ attabiAAu m_a_ yoo_ha_ ilayya min rabbee h_atha_ ba_sa_-iru min rabbikum wahudan wara_h_matun liqawmin yu\minoon*a*
